description:
Turing Network is a high-performance public blockchain project, enabling mobile internet users get access to the blockchain and crypto

system.Focusing on the developer's benefits, Turing Network's blockchain framwork provides complete suites for mobile internet developers to transfer mobile internet user's rights and assets to Turing blockchain system, which help internet users move to the blockchain world smoothly and enjoy the blockchian business value. Turing Network is initiated in Oct 2018，and Turing public blockchain TestNet is expected to be released in Oct 2019. Meanwhile, Turing Foundation gives great importance to the community development. Through motivation mechanism, Turing Foundation encourages outstanding developers to join and support Turing Blockchain and Turing Ecosystem's sustainable development.
name: TuringNetworkToken
